#### Huber loss
- created in **1964**
- a combination of **MSE** and **MAE**
- for "robust regression" (less sensitive to outlier, than squared error loss ((M?)SE))
- can be modified for classification
- defined piecewise
- links :
	- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Huber_loss
